The '''C-6 [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]]''' was a household [[Droid/Legends|droid]] programmed with many functions and different forms of communication. It was manufactured by [[Cybot Galactica/Legends|Cybot Galactica]] on the factory moon of [[Telti/Legends|Telti]] in the time of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. It was the predecessor of the [[C-7 protocol droid]] and the successor of the [[C-5 protocol droid]]

